basics.name: Davin Takahashi
basics.label: Student
basics.summary: I am working towards a B.S. in Computer Science in the Department of Information and Computer Sciences at the University of Hawaii at Manoa. I expect to graduate in Spring, 2021. I am interested in learning how technology can be used for interdisciplinary analysis, and garnering creative insights.
